{"tid":1592639,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［討論］十月一日點搞！！！","createTime":"2019-09-24T16:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T17:55:48.000Z","uid":207143,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f73d16e22bb31827a6d65b5b7f82236c34c1542a","tid":1592639,"uid":207143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:56:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地要快啲討論好十月一號嘅行動方向<br />\n麻煩唔好再推啲無謂po上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n <br />\n點解要諗定當日行動？已經有民陣搞遊行啦？<br />\n因為我相信黑警一撚定唔會批港島遊行<br />\n就算我地堅持去都有重兵部署好<br />\n再將港島變孤島 就全世界等比人拉<br />\n<br />\n雖然我知大家對港島有種情意結<br />\n而且港島又有支聯辦狗總政總垃圾會<br />\n可以話係對準權力核心 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係大家唔可以再沉醉係港島開戰</span><br />\n<br />\n所以我地一定要改變策略<br />\n之前見到都有唔同手足諗到幾個大方向<br />\n希望各連登手足盡快討論並決定好<br />\n等文宣組可以吹大雞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 參考8月5日三罷經驗，遍地開花[</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 九龍區大遊行 eg:旺角、尖咀、黃大仙</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 「和你塞」全世界入機場</span><br />\n<br />\n大家快啲諗下邊個好啲再快啲決定啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1668baa75824bc46c3ca2c891aa2bbf2227786","tid":1592639,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"b319fd34df0935aee230bad132b8a0a0b8e9516e","tid":1592639,"uid":207143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:57:01.000Z","msg":"10月1 推"},{"pid":"35e06f92d4ec4a8d460b378855fa26e91ac958cb","tid":1592639,"uid":207143,"like":0,"dislike":0