2]<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: violet;\">以「香港全民議政會」投票及發佈Channel投票：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUhvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=c1193985\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a> [3]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">投票需要你：</span></span><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: violet;\">加入Channel：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUhvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=c1193985\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: violet;\">投票</span><br />\n3. <span style=\"color: violet;\">叫朋友</span>加入Channel一起投票！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&lt;感謝支持&gt;</span></span><br />\n集合全港多名設計精英，文宣組共設計了七款 Logo，在此先向這些有心人<span style=\"color: violet;\">致謝</span>。<br />\n希望藉著這次投票，和大家一起開始建立<span style=\"color: violet;\">真正屬於香港人的民主議政平台</span>。<br />\n隨人數增加、平台民主及身份認證制度變得完善，希望HK Assembly將變得更具公信力，讓大家<span style=\"color: violet;\">投票救港</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">HK Assembly Logo投票Link：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUhvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=c1193985\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n- - - - - - - - - -<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">隨意門：《香港全民議政會》 HK Assembly 正式成立 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1590386/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1590386/page/1</a><br />\n- - - - - - - - - -<br />\n[1] 暫時未有機制解決Telegram上一人多號引致一人多票的身份認證問題，但：<br />\n1. 這是初期階段未能解決的複雜問題<br />\n2. 估計一人多號佔使用者比例不高<br />\n3. 因為抵消效果，減少對投票結果影響<br />\n4. 對此投票問題，控制投票結果的誘因不大<br />\n[2] 兩款設計交由設計師作最後加工後，第二輛投票預計於29/9進行<br />\n[3]<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 無Telegram？【趁而家快D裝啦！】</span></span>隨人數增加、平台民主及身份認證制度變得完善，希望HK Assembly將變得更具公信力，讓大家投票救港！"},{"pid":"4b6c099fec6a70f157c8f8708bf4e16e0e444885","tid":1592639,"uid":144433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:00:18.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n4/10"},{"pid":"59fd88ba394a086f5c97187d96ab3d9a8d04314f","tid":1592639,"uid":144433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n5/10"},{"pid":"850df28cb5aaff7166a5d581eb105cdae78efcc9","tid":1592639,"uid":144433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:00:43.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n6/10"},{"pid":"262d26be6550bf2b0ca05faef80bc85704945b11","tid":1592639,"uid":144433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:00:53.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n7/10"},{"pid":"1bd9ad78d6ee2fe3c54befef271217c5317fadd4","tid":1592639,"uid":207143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:00:55.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"f49ab5e4756368f35ad0d809efebe8f209be355d","tid":1592639,"uid":144433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:01:03.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n8/10"}]}